===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|hleahtor||laughter, jubilation, derision|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*hlahtraz||laughter}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*klek-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*kleg-||to shout}}. Cognate with German {{term|Gelächter||laughter, hilarity, merriment|lang=de}}, Danish and Norwegian {{term|latter||laughter|lang=da}}, Icelandic {{term|hlátur||laughter|lang=is}}. More at {{l|en|laugh}}.

